<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>生日 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5/</link><description>Recent content in 生日 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2025 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 May 2011 15:25:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><follow_challenge><feedId>42331815237783556</feedId><userId>41909911558319104</userId></follow_challenge><item><title>2011.05.22</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/birth/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 May 2011 15:25:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/birth/</guid><description>祝你生日快乐，愿这一天充满欢乐与美好回忆！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/birth/featured.png"/></item><item><title>妈妈 生日快乐</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-mother/</link><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jan 2011 12:02:55 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-mother/</guid><description>清晨通话时得知家乡连日大雪，屋内炉火温暖家人围坐谈笑，思念瞬间涌上心头。去年缺席母亲生日和春节，今年归家仍是奢望，电话里强忍哽咽只报平安。母亲总以儿女为先，近年才懂她默默承受的压力。亲人离世教会我行孝需及时，如今惟愿家人安康。虽无法当面诉说，仍想对母亲道声生日快乐与爱意。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-mother/featured.png"/></item><item><title>妹妹 生日快乐</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-sister/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Dec 2010 12:19:44 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-sister/</guid><description>QQ 邮箱的生日提醒让“我”猛然意识到许久未联系妹妹和家人，陷入深深自责。回忆童年时对妹妹的伤害，尤其是用锤子误伤她手指的愧疚至今萦绕心头，而妹妹始终毫无怨言。儿时因性格怪戾疏于关怀，如今才懂她独自承受的艰辛，包括可能遭遇的校园欺凌。成长中的创伤让“我”变得敏感，但妹妹的孩子对“我”天然亲近又带来慰藉。最后真挚祝福妹妹生日快乐，字里行间满是迟来的歉意与手足深情！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-sister/featured.png"/></item><item><title>爸爸 生日快乐</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-father/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Sep 2010 09:26:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-father/</guid><description>去年生日为父亲买了蛋糕却因今年经济拮据无法准备礼物，内心充满愧疚。电话中听到父亲爽朗的饮酒声，感受到两代人无需言语的默契与快乐传染的力量。虽羞于当面表达，但那份父子间的挂念与祝福始终深藏心底。生日快乐！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-father/featured.png"/></item><item><title>福福 生日快乐</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-fufu/</link><pubDate>Wed, 15 Sep 2010 09:15:06 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-fufu/</guid><description>第一眼相遇便心生喜欢，那份悸动仿佛命中注定。虽相隔遥远，仍想亲口对你说声生日快乐！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/happy-birthday-to-my-fufu/featured.png"/></item><item><title>祝妈妈生日快乐.!</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/i-wish-my-mother-a-happy-birthday/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Dec 2008 23:55:43 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/i-wish-my-mother-a-happy-birthday/</guid><description>妈妈 47 岁生日因参加表哥喜宴无法回家，电话里叮嘱她好好过。数着妈妈的白发才惊觉时光飞逝，自己已 20 岁。记忆中父母从未争吵，妈妈隐忍善良的形象始终鲜明。虽今年缺席，但承诺明年无论多远必归，因为这天比过年更珍贵。刚通话时妈妈仍在忙碌，父母低调从不张扬生日，唯愿能陪伴左右。祝妈妈生日快乐！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/i-wish-my-mother-a-happy-birthday/featured.png"/></item><item><title>醉</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/drunks/</link><pubDate>Tue, 16 Dec 2008 22:26:33 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/drunks/</guid><description>昨晚醉酒后仍坚持写日记，虽内容寥寥却心念此事。陈过生日时已不胜酒力，今后饮酒绝不再兑其他饮品，誓死不从！</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/drunks/featured.png"/></item><item><title>昨天喝醉了... 貌似...</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/drunk-yesterday/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Oct 2008 11:50:04 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/drunk-yesterday/</guid><description>ZS 生日聚会上混饮啤酒和二锅头导致醉酒，醒后需要保持清醒。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/drunk-yesterday/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>